# Implementation Plan: 16-bit 2.5D Racing Game

## Goal Description
Create a retro-style racing game that mimics the "Mode 7" depth effect found in 16-bit console games (like Mario Kart). This serves as a creative "checkpoint" and demonstrating agentic coding capabilities.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> I will use **generic assets** (geometric shapes and generated patterns) instead of copyrighted Nintendo characters or sprites. I will simulate the *style* and *feel* of the 16-bit era.

