#### [NEW] [game.js](file:///c:/Users/eqhsp/.gemini/antigravity/brain/4d84e3fc-4182-44ee-8105-bdd244f7bb40/mk_checkpoint/game.js)
The core game engine.
*   **Loop**: standard `requestAnimationFrame`.
*   **Renderer**: distinct "Mode 7" projection algorithm:
    *   Iterate screen scanlines (y-axis).
    *   Calculate depth (Z) for each scanline.
    *   Project track coordinates (Map X, Map Y) based on Player position and Angle.
    *   Sample from a "Track Map" (grid or texture).
*   **Player**: 2D handling physics (acceleration, drifting friction).
*   **Sprites**: Draw objects with scale `1/Z`.

#### [NEW] [assets.js](file:///c:/Users/eqhsp/.gemini/antigravity/brain/4d84e3fc-4182-44ee-8105-bdd244f7bb40/mk_checkpoint/assets.js)
Generates the track map texture and sprite data programmatically to keep the project standalone.

